messages.title: YOUR CHOICE AT THIS ELECTION:
messages.content: STRONG, STABLE LEADERSHIP OF THE NATIONAL INTEREST OR A COALITION OF CHAOS WITH JEREMY CORBYN

keyPolicies.policyTitle: MAKING BREXIT A SUCCESS IS CENTRAL TO OUR NATIONAL INTEREST
keyPolicies.policyDescription: Making Brexit a success is central to our national interest, and that starts with confirming the democratic decision produced by the referendum.
Backing Enterprise, we are going to have to keep our economy strong.
Sustainable Development, homes for the future, creating jobs for the local residents and protecting our beautiful living environment.
